title: Courgette Herb Bread
ingredients: ['100ml (4 fl oz) water', '1 dessertspoon honey', '1 tablespoon vegetable oil', '75g (3 oz) grated courgette', '75g (3 oz) wholemeal flour', '275g (10 oz) bread flour', 'small handful chopped fresh basil', '1 dessertspoon sesame seeds', '1 teaspoon salt', '1 1/2 teaspoons dried active baking yeast']
